Description: 
Developed a centralized ERP platform for attendance synchronization and enterprise operations using ASP.NET MVC 5, C#, and 
SQL Server. Implemented RBAC, OAuth authentication, and admin dashboard with user/company and tool access control. 
Built key modules including attendance processing, branch issue detection, reprocessing, salary garbage anomaly validation, 
employee reporting & Analytics System (RDLC) and multi-database management. Enhanced system efficiency through data monitoring, 
performance optimization, and secure architecture, ensuring high data integrity and reliable ERP operations.
